341
00:26:42,949 --> 00:26:44,719
No. I'm scared.

342
00:26:45,018 --> 00:26:47,459
What eternal luxury
did I want to enjoy...

343
00:26:48,488 --> 00:26:51,088
that I married the
sister of King Hades?

