345
00:26:59,369 --> 00:27:02,038
It's ginseng chicken soup. It's
good for you and delicious.

346
00:27:02,169 --> 00:27:04,669
But why are you
buying this for me?

347
00:27:05,538 --> 00:27:08,649
I think I've misjudged
you a little.

348
00:27:12,419 --> 00:27:13,679
