363
00:28:14,238 --> 00:28:15,808
As if there could be anything.

364
00:28:36,268 --> 00:28:38,429
<font color="#00ff00">LEE RANG</font>

365
00:28:41,498 --> 00:28:44,068
The person you have
reached is not available.

366
