drop dead at any second,

433
00:32:15,849 --> 00:32:17,149
so shut it.

434
00:32:18,488 --> 00:32:20,018
What the...

435
00:32:20,588 --> 00:32:21,689
Where are your manners?

436
00:32:23,889 --> 00:32:26,558
